1. install NOOBS

2. apt-get update

3. sudo apt-get install mysql-server-5.5 libmysqlclient-dev libconfig++-dev gcc-avr arduino vim screen libjson-perl

4. run 'raspi-config', go to advanced settings to enable SPI

5. disable serial console in /etc/inittab, replace with "T0:23:respawn:/usr/bin/screen -S hub-avr-monitor /dev/ttyO1 57600"
